To build this software please run:

make TOOLCHAIN=/path/to/your/toolchain TRIPLET=your-target-triplet

You may as well optionally use:

CFLAGS=<your-gcc-flags>
CXXFLAGS=<your-g++-flags>
LDFLAGS=<your-linker-flags>

with limited set of compiler or linker flags.

If you just run `make` this software will be built natively by your system compiler.

The act-server binary and coresponding act-client files are placed in act-server/build directory.

